<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This Standard is prescribed in accordance with the provisions of Article 17 of the Act Governing Food Sanitation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The classification of vegetables, fruits, herbs and spices,which are referred in the Standards for maximum tolerance of heavy metals in plant origin are listed in the Appendix.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Maximum tolerance of heavy metals in edible plant origin shall meet the following Table:(wet weight basis)

┌─────────────────┬──────┬─────┐
│              ＼　Heavymetal      │Cadmium     │Lead      │
│FoodCategory    ＼                │            │          │
├─────────────────┼──────┼─────┤
│Leafy vegetables                  │0.2   ppm   │0.3   ppm │
├─────────────────┼──────┼─────┤
│Brassica vegetables               │0.05  ppm   │0.3   ppm │
├─────────────────┼──────┼─────┤
│Root and tuber vegetables, Stalk  │0.1   ppm   │0.3   ppm │
│and stem vegetables               │            │          │
│(not to includeBulb vegetables)   │            │          │
├─────────────────┼──────┼─────┤
│Bulb vegetables                   │0.05  ppm   │0.1   ppm │
├─────────────────┼──────┼─────┤
│Fruiting vegetables               │0.05  ppm   │0.1   ppm │
├─────────────────┼──────┼─────┤
│Pulses and Legume Vegetables      │0.2   ppm   │0.2   ppm │
├─────────────────┼──────┼─────┤
│Berries and other small fruits    │0.05  ppm   │0.2   ppm │
├─────────────────┼──────┼─────┤
│Citrus fruits                     │0.05  ppm   │0.1   ppm │
├─────────────────┼──────┼─────┤
│Pome fruits                       │0.05  ppm   │0.1   ppm │
├─────────────────┼──────┼─────┤
│Stone fruits                      │0.05  ppm   │0.1   ppm │
├─────────────────┼──────┼─────┤
│Melons                            │0.05  ppm   │0.1   ppm │
├─────────────────┼──────┼─────┤
│Other assorted (sub)tropical      │0.05  ppm   │0.1   ppm │
│fruits                            │            │          │
├─────────────────┼──────┼─────┤
│Herbs and Spices (fresh)          │0.2   ppm   │0.3   ppm │
└─────────────────┴──────┴─────┘

]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This Standard shall be implemented from June 1, 2011.
The amended articles hereof shall come into effect as of the day of promulgation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
</法規>
